| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-2617 — Recovery Inhibition (incransom)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 5d85a780-a0f9-54e4-b8b7-8cc4e592d89e"
